  "texts": [
    "For example, performance of the models significantly improves when chain of thought (CoT) prompting is used.",
    "CoT can be thought of as a step-by-step problem-solving process in which the LLM argues with itself simulating a set of experts.",
    "Under this scenario, the model is given the problem in small chunks before the eventual answer is reached by consensus among the experts.",
    "Using the described setting Enigma base (CoT) model obtained 88.28% accuracy.",
    "When a larger model is used with CoT, Enigma Large 's accuracy achieves its best scoring, 97.51%, surpassing human performance for the first time."
  ],
